{"tid":1452978,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「溫故知新」逃犯條例惡果","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:02:32.000Z","uid":185375,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1f5e39a52b510e233d8199486e2a2034349bd3","tid":1452978,"uid":185375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"反修例活動已經過左兩個月<br />\n<br />\n政府一度避開問題重心，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對逃犯條例，撤回惡法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n經歷多次大型民意遊行，政府不但無回應，仲加劇民怨。截至8月11日，已經見證警察多次不依警察條例，香港法例執法。一旦惡法通過，只會產生更多越法及莫須有罪名。網上一直流傳不同惡法下會發生後果，以下係我覺得最直接影響市民嘅嚴重後果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xr3uKXA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXr3uKXA.png&h=40fc67ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ea7jnKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEa7jnKg.png&h=a551370d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJ2CTQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJ2CTQX.png&h=8e469ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6cfFvX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6cfFvX.png&h=4148d863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XA3B9pi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXA3B9pi.png&h=1a18b42e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZbzV4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZbzV4i.png&h=f339a0ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLyFRCE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLyFRCE.png&h=8bd130bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouC7wCF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouC7wCF.png&h=0f651958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5RgpXF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5RgpXF.png&h=2527d566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獲得通過後嘅法例將會以行政長官就單一案件提交嘅方式移交被告，移交控罪除咗謀殺罪同誤殺罪之外，亦包埋賄賂、欺詐出入境當局等卅幾項<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可判監7年或以上嘅控罪</span></span>，香港政府亦可協助中國大陸等地凍結沒收喺香港嘅財產。草案一提出，就惹來社會各方質疑同關切香港作為獨立司法管轄區嘅獨立性或者遭到削弱。<br />\n<br />\n而根據中華人民共和國刑法第234條的規定，犯故意傷害罪的，<br />\n（致人輕傷的）處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或者管制；<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">致人重傷的，處3年以上10年以下有期徒刑；</span><br />\n致人死亡或者以特別殘忍手段致人重傷造成嚴重殘疾的，處10年以上有期徒刑、無期徒刑或者死刑。<br />\n<br />\n政府既然可以容許香港警察做出越法及不合規嘅行為，就算發生圖中情況也不稀奇。<br />\n<br />\n請分享至各方朋友跟家人，喚醒大家需守護香港嘅心！<br />\n<br />\nResource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/588359434562420/posts/2442315175833494?s=1665355263&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F588359434562420%2Fposts%2F2442315175833494%3Fs%3D1665355263%26sfns%3Dmo&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkfPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=98a5d3db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/588359434562420/posts/2442315175833494?s=1665355263&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ff910bf04b1298ccfb32f5d68a32612a034a43fb","tid":1452978,"uid":185375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:55:44.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"48f12032e6ff6aa2512023e9c7eb32b41779778a","tid":1452978,"uid":185375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:56:26.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"39adbb11c4118f5acdd626e1a491b445dd574ad2","tid":1452978,"uid":185375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"d9933ada7365797abfbe528a43ae7f4380934a22","tid":1452978,"uid":185375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"89ff8368112fe9784e063584007e651fe6a2c56e","tid":1452978,"uid":259812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"cfa434dc3a2db8e10887e5c5826f85be6def429c","tid":1452978,"u